ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would recommend this class to any student who is interested in political competition. As an econ student, I have no background in political science, but I still enjoyed this class very much.
Useful for anyone interested in formal modeling.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: The course was interesting and inspiring. I often came up with new ideas during class discussion. The models we learned were useful and applicable to other settings.
Most of the material was not directly relevant to my research, but I learned a lot about formal modeling.
I am not in political science department, so this question is not applicable to me.
